{#-
  Tag — labelled chip with optional iconLeading and opt-in dismiss button.

  Composes Badge visual envelope (rounded pill, 6 variants × {solid, soft})
  + a leading icon slot (Lucide curated set) + an opt-in dismiss button
  ('×' icon-only, calls tag-dismiss controller). The dismiss is opt-in via
  `dismissable: true` per OQ-mini Tag doctrine sealed S2.6 — the default
  Tag is read-only (no controller, no dismiss button, no JS), matching the
  "smallest viable surface + opt-in via prop" doctrine.

  Visual difference from Badge :
   - Tag size scale is sm | md | lg (one extra step) — Tag is the labelling
     primitive used in dense contexts (cards, table rows, filter pills).
   - Tag carries an opt-in dismiss button (alert-dismiss S1.4b pattern
     mirror via tag-dismiss controller).
   - Tag is intended to be interactive in clusters (filter pills) — Badge
     is purely informational.

  Parameters:
    variant     (string, optional) default | primary | success | warning | danger | info
    size        (string, optional) sm | md (default) | lg
    label       (string, required) the visible text (consumer-resolved)
    leadingIcon (string, optional) Lucide icon name from src/assets/icons/
    soft        (bool,   optional) default false. true → uses *-soft pair
    dismissable (bool,   optional) default false. true → render '×' button +
                                    wire tag-dismiss controller
    dismissAria (string, optional) accessible name for the dismiss button.
                                    Falls back to 'theme.tag.aria.dismiss'
                                    interpolated with `label`.
    className   (string, optional)
-#}

{%- set variant     = variant     | default('default') -%}
{%- set size        = size        | default('md') -%}
{%- set label       = label       | default('') -%}
{%- set leadingIcon = leadingIcon | default(null) -%}
{%- set soft        = soft        | default(false) -%}
{%- set dismissable = dismissable | default(false) -%}
{%- set dismissAria = dismissAria | default(null) -%}
{%- set className   = className   | default('') -%}

{%- set _classes = ['theme-tag'] -%}
{%- if className -%}{%- set _classes = _classes | merge([className]) -%}{%- endif -%}

{%- set _effectiveDismissAria = dismissAria ?? ('theme.tag.aria.dismiss'|trans({ '%label%': label })) -%}

<span
  class="{{ _classes | join(' ') }}"
  data-variant="{{ variant }}"
  data-size="{{ size }}"
  {%- if soft %} data-soft="true"{% endif -%}
  {%- if dismissable %} data-controller="tag-dismiss" data-tag-dismiss-label-value="{{ label }}"{% endif -%}
>
  {%- if leadingIcon -%}
    {% include '@theme/components/icon/icon.html.twig' with { name: leadingIcon, decorative: true, size: size == 'sm' ? 'xs' : (size == 'lg' ? 'sm' : 'xs') } %}
  {%- endif -%}
  <span class="theme-tag__label">{{ label }}</span>
  {%- if dismissable -%}
    <button
      type="button"
      class="theme-tag__dismiss"
      aria-label="{{ _effectiveDismissAria }}"
      data-action="click->tag-dismiss#dismiss"
    >
      <span aria-hidden="true">×</span>
    </button>
  {%- endif -%}
</span>
